## üß© Circuit Schematic (Breadboard Layout) ‚Äî **As specified in the thesis**

The table below follows the wiring described in the thesis (Biometric Health Data Measurement with Live Broadcast). Citations to the thesis are included for each device.

### üì∫ ST7789 TFT Display (ST7789, 240√ó320 / 2.0")
| TFT Pin | ESP32 Pin | Notes |
|--------:|:---------:|:-----|
| VCC     | 3.3V      | Power (3.3V). :contentReference[oaicite:6]{index=6} |
| GND     | GND       | Ground. :contentReference[oaicite:7]{index=7} |
| SCL (SCK) | GPIO 18 | SPI Clock. :contentReference[oaicite:8]{index=8} |
| SDA (MOSI)| GPIO 23 | SPI MOSI / Data. :contentReference[oaicite:9]{index=9} |
| RES     | GPIO 4    | Reset. :contentReference[oaicite:10]{index=10} |
| DC      | GPIO 2    | Data/Command. :contentReference[oaicite:11]{index=11} |
| CS      | GPIO 5    | Chip Select. :contentReference[oaicite:12]{index=12} |
| BLK     | 3.3V (or via resistor/driver) | Backlight (depends on module). :contentReference[oaicite:13]{index=13} |

