### ‚ù§Ô∏è MAX30100 (Pulse Oximeter)
| MAX30100 Pin | ESP32 Pin | Notes |
|-------------:|:---------:|:-----|
| VIN          | 3.3V      | Power (thesis uses 3.3V). :contentReference[oaicite:14]{index=14} |
| GND          | GND       | Ground. :contentReference[oaicite:15]{index=15} |
| SDA          | GPIO 21   | I2C SDA shared bus. :contentReference[oaicite:16]{index=16} |
| SCL          | GPIO 22   | I2C SCL shared bus. :contentReference[oaicite:17]{index=17} |
| INT          | (Not used) | Optional interrupt ‚Äî leave disconnected unless used. :contentReference[oaicite:18]{index=18} |

---

### üå°Ô∏è MLX90614 (IR Temperature)
| MLX90614 Pin | ESP32 Pin | Notes |
|-------------:|:---------:|:-----|
| VDD / VCC    | **5V** *or* **3.3V** | Thesis wiring uses **5V**; module is specified 3‚Äì5V (check your breakout). If the module's datasheet/breakout requires 5V, use 5V. If the breakout supports 3.3V I2C, prefer **3.3V** to keep I2C levels consistent with ESP32. :contentReference[oaicite:19]{index=19} |
| GND          | GND       | Ground. :contentReference[oaicite:20]{index=20} |
| SDA          | GPIO 21   | I2C SDA (shared with MAX30100). :contentReference[oaicite:21]{index=21} |
| SCL          | GPIO 22   | I2C SCL (shared). :contentReference[oaicite:22]{index=22} |

**Important:** The thesis lists **VDD ‚Üí 5V** for the MLX90614 wiring. That is acceptable for many GY-906 breakouts, but check your exact breakout‚Äôs datasheet. If your breakout‚Äôs logic lines are NOT 3.3V-tolerant when VDD=5V, either use 3.3V VDD or add an I2C level shifter. :contentReference[oaicite:23]{index=23}

---

### üìà AD8232 (ECG)
| AD8232 Pin | ESP32 Pin | Notes |
|-----------:|:---------:|:-----|
| VDD        | 3.3V      | Power. :contentReference[oaicite:24]{index=24} |
| GND        | GND       | Ground. :contentReference[oaicite:25]{index=25} |
| OUT        | GPIO 34   | Analog ECG signal (ADC). :contentReference[oaicite:26]{index=26} |
| LO+        | GPIO 33   | Lead-off + (optional/useful). :contentReference[oaicite:27]{index=27} |
| LO-        | GPIO 32   | Lead-off - (optional/useful). :contentReference[oaicite:28]{index=28} |

